you'll learn nothing but bad habits.

625
00:47:23,040 --> 00:47:25,941
Okay, it's time for your lessons.

626
00:47:26,009 --> 00:47:28,273
Let's see what you've learned.

627
00:47:29,780 --> 00:47:32,772
