That always gets them.

628
00:47:32,850 --> 00:47:37,310
And while you're at it, pray that
Mrs. Simpson remembers to show up.

629
00:47:50,200 --> 00:47:51,861
Lover boy.

630
00:47:51,935 --> 00:47:53,869
